                     <interp inst="t18460615-1311-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>for stealing 1 promissory-note for 5<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18460615-name-542" type="victimName">
